entries.femaleVariant: Hey, you chose it. Mine was fine.
Yeah, well, you'd eat anything, wouldn't you?
Sure, I guess, except... asparagus. I don't like asparagus.
Oh really? When's the last time you saw asparagus?!
What else're you not a fan of, hm? White truffles?
I dunno... I just know I don't like asparagus. What's wrong with that?
